title: Bug 121170 - getColumnLabel should return recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned by IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before extraction are null, while the labels after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: The labels returned by IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before and after extraction should both be recognizable strings.
SR: To reproduce the bug, call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before and after data extraction and compare the results.
